  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This two arms parallel cluster-randomized trial will evaluate the impact of a customized&#xD;
      coaching program for surgeons on the occurrence of patient major adverse events. Trends in&#xD;
      surgical outcomes before and after the intervention will be compared between surgeons&#xD;
      randomly assigned to the coaching program against non-exposed surgeons.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
